OL,5,G2100 Ambulance: Code Red
OL,6,     FAfter a woman suffers cardiac
OL,7,     Farrest while driving, paramedics
OL,8,     Fmust induce a coma at the roadside
OL,9,     Fto save her. Meanwhile, a
OL,10,     F19-year-old suffers critical
OL,11,     Finjuries in a motorcycle crash.
OL,12,G2200 Ambulance: Code Red
OL,13,     FParamedics rush to help a
OL,14,     F67-year-old HGV driver who has
OL,15,     Fsuffered a cardiac arrest, and, in
OL,16,     FHillingdon, a man who has suffered
OL,17,     Fsevere burns after lighting a
OL,18,     Fbonfire with petrol.
