OL,5,G2300 Skin A&E
OL,6,     FDr Dev Shah treats a Nottingham
OL,7,     FForest fan with a large head cyst,
OL,8,     Fand Dr Toby Nelson deals with a
OL,9,     Fseries of mini lipomas that look
OL,10,     Flike a string of pearls.
OL,11,G0000 Killer at the Crime Scene
OL,12,     FWhen 82-year-old Mohammed Saleem
OL,13,     Fis fatally stabbed in Birmingham
OL,14,     Fand a series of explosions targets
OL,15,     Fmosques in the West Midlands,
OL,16,     Fcounter terrorism uncovers a
OL,17,     Fhate-fueled campaign.
OL,18,G0100 Police Interceptors
OL,19,     FA runaway driver escapes the car
OL,20,     Fwhile still on the move, leaving
OL,21,     FKev to chase him down on foot.
